Package: iNEXT.4steps
Type: Package
Title: Four Steps of Interpolation and Extrapolation Analysis
Version: 1.0.0
Author: Anne Chao and Kai-Hsiang Hu
Maintainer: Anne Chao <chao@stat.nthu.edu.tw>
URL: https://chao.stat.nthu.edu.tw/wordpress/software_download/inext-4steps/
Description: iNEXT.4steps provides a simple function to create a complete analysis process
             with following four parts:
             Step1: Sample completeness profiles.
             Step2: Asymptotic analysis.
             Step3: Non-asymptotic coverage-based rarefaction and extrapolation analysis.
             Step4: Evenness among species abundances.
             You can input some easy setting to change the calculations.
             The result contains a summary table and a figures.
             (You can find the paper(No.135) from Chao proffessor's website:
             http://chao.stat.nthu.edu.tw/wordpress/publication-list/).
License: GPL (>= 3)
